          '<p class="mb-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Use <code>.navbar-expand-lg</code> to control when the navbar collapses into a hamburger menu. Combine with <code>.navbar-dark</code> or <code>.navbar-light</code> and a <code>bg-*</code> class for theming.</p>',
