          '<p class="mb-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">The hamburger toggler uses <code>.navbar-toggler</code> with <code>data-bs-toggle="collapse"</code> and <code>data-bs-target</code>. The collapsible wrapper is <code>.collapse.navbar-collapse</code>.</p>',
