          '<p class="mb-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Tooltips use <code>data-bs-toggle="tooltip"</code> with <code>title</code> attribute content. They must be initialized via JavaScript: <code>new bootstrap.Tooltip(element)</code>, or select all with <code>[data-bs-toggle="tooltip"]</code>.</p>',
          '<p class="mb-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Popovers are expanded tooltips with a header and body. Use <code>data-bs-toggle="popover"</code> with <code>data-bs-title</code> and <code>data-bs-content</code>. They also require JS initialization. Control placement with <code>data-bs-placement="top|bottom|left|right"</code>.</p>',
