          '  <p class="text-blue-800 font-medium"><i class="fa-solid fa-lightbulb text-blue-500"></i> Key Insight: Tooltips and popovers are opt-in for performance. You must initialize them. A common pattern is: <code>document.querySelectorAll(\'[data-bs-toggle="tooltip"]\').forEach(el => new bootstrap.Tooltip(el))</code>.</p>',
          '</div>',
          '<pre class="bg-gray-900 text-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg overflow-x-auto text-sm mb-4"><code>&lt;button data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="I am a tooltip"&gt;Hover me&lt;/button&gt;',
