          '<p class="mb-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Toasts are lightweight notifications similar to mobile push notifications. They\'re built with <code>.toast</code> containing <code>.toast-header</code> and <code>.toast-body</code>. Toasts are hidden by default and shown with JS.</p>',
          '<p class="mb-3 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Show a toast with <code>new bootstrap.Toast(element).show()</code>. Control auto-hide with <code>data-bs-autohide="false"</code> and delay with <code>data-bs-delay="5000"</code>. Stack multiple toasts using a <code>.toast-container</code> with position-fixed.</p>',
